parameters: \n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Thank you for saving Peeko...\.\.\. Peeko,\. you saved.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Looks like that plant's gone for good.\.\. You're safe now...
\n<\n[1]>Heh~\. Gardening or monsters,\. everything doesn't like being cut down huh~\.
At the sound of a strange voice,\. Neneko begins to look around...\.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Peeko didn't get eaten!\.\. She saved them!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\N[1]>Urgh...\.\.\. what are you people saying?\.\. It's bothering my ears...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>The cave maw?\.\. What,\. this dumb big mouthed plant thing?\.\. That was nothing.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>The cursed one's a hero!\.\. A hero!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
A bunch of strange tiny people have shown up.\.\. It's pretty obvious none of them are human considering their furry lower bodies,\. black eyes,\. and horns.\.\.
The fact that they were speaking gibberish didn't really do anything to make Neneko less agitated.\.\.
But Neneko was confused.\.\. She was still tiny,\. wasn't she?\.\. Wouldn't that mean these guys were this size normally?\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Come and celebrate with us,\. Cursed One!\.\. Many food and drinks to celebrate getting our home back!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Wh-\. hey!\.\. Let go of me!\.\. Who the hell do you think you are?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Dangit,\. you guys are way too forceful!\.\. Treat yer hero with some respect!\.\.
Neneko lets out a threatening hiss,\. but the weird little people didn't seem to pay her any mind as they surrounded her,\. leading her deeper into the tiny cave.\.\.
Neneko's eyes widened at the sight of what awaited her.\.\.
Despite her complaining,\. the strange mini people continue to cheer and lead her along to this so-\.called celebration.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Listen,\. ya can thank me all ya want but I've got places to...\.\.\. be...\.\.\.
Neneko's eyes widened at the sight of what awaited her.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>We're going to celebrate with flap flap meat!\.\. Come join us!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
The small monster girl pointed at the huge slab of meat hanging over a fire ahead of them,\. smiling brightly towards Neneko.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Flap flap meat...\.\.\. er...\.\.\. that must be a bird right?\.\. Oh,\. damn,\. I guess a bird at this size would be a giant monster...\.\.\.
Neneko hoped she wasn't drooling.\.\. It would be bad to show weakness.\.\. Considering the way they were all giggling,\. she probably failed.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>The cursed one looks like she likes flap flap meat!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Well she can have as much as she likes,\. yes!\.\. She's a friend of the Lilis now!\.\. Tonight will be a feast!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
The strange mini people scatter,\. dancing,\. drinking,\. eating,\. or some combination of the three,\. leaving Neneko to watch on.\.\.
The Lilis scatter,\. dancing,\. drinking,\. eating,\. or some combination of the three,\. leaving Neneko with just the one girl who had been holding her hand on the way there.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Come and have fun fun with us!\.\. You're invited to our home whenever you want!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Eh?\.\. I don't get what you're saying,\. girl!\.\.
\n<\n[1]>A friend of the Lilis,\. huh...?\.\. So you're not joking about this feast,\. right?\.\
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>No jokes at all!~\.\.\. Stick around,\. yes yes!~\.\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
The girl giggles,\. letting go of Neneko's hand and running off to join the others.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Wow...\.\.\. this is definitely some kind of feast.\.\. I don't get it,\. it was just a plant?\.\.
She looks at the festivities.\.\. There are a few eyes on her,\. but for the most part no one seems to really care.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Man,\. who'd have thought there were a bunch of little people out here...\.\.\.\BST[1,Neneko2] guess you wouldn't really know without this shrinking thing...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Hmph.\.\. Whatever.\.\. I don't really have the time for this.\.\.
Man,\. who'd have thought there were a bunch of little people out here...\.\.\. they called themselves Lilis right?\.\. Wonder if anyone else knows they're here.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Ah well.\.\. At least they're friendlier than the people in the city.\.\. Can't say I've ever been offered free food before.\.\. Having people who owe me ain't a bad thing~\.
Neneko's eyes go back to that gigantic stick of meat.\.\. The scent alone was making her drool again...\.\.\.
It probably came from a normal sized animal,\. but shrunken down like this,\. that one chunk of meat looked big enough to live off of for a month...!\.\.
\n<\n[1]>...\.\.\.M-\.maybe I could stick around for a bit...\.\.\.\BST[1] nothin'll get done on an empty stomach...\.\.\. and free food is free food...!!!\.\.
It's definitely bird meat...\.\.\. nice and thick and juicy too...\.\.\. These Lilis really knew how to cook!\.\.
It probably came from a normal sized animal,\. but shrunken down like this,\. that one chunk of meat looked big enough to live off of for a month...!\.\.
\n<???>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Peeko danger!\.\. Huge Cave Maw wanna eat eat!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<???>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Go kill Cave Maw!\.\. Go save friend!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]

\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>You're the friendliest Cursed One I've ever seen~\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Cut it out with the gibberish.\.\. If ya've got something to say then say it!\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Why do you guys keep calling me a Cursed One?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>!\.\. Wait...\.\.\. you talkin' about my ears,\. eh!?\.\.\BST[3] That it?\.\. Ya got a problem!?\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Mmmm,\. you're still jumpy though~\. Hey,\. hey,\. where's the rest of your tribe?\.\. I've never heard of any tribes near here!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Tribe?\.\. I don't got...\.\.\. tsk,\. right,\. I've still got business down there...\.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Peeko was a goner,\. for sure,\. but then you swish swished in and killed the cave maw invading our home!\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>You're a hero,\. a hero!\.\. Come dance with us!~\.\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Oy,\. hands off unless you're picking a fight!!\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Awww~\. She's shy!\.\. Boo!\.\. Boo!\.\. Dance anyway!~\.\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>A hero huh...?\.\. First time I've ever heard that.\.\.\.\BST[5,Neneko] Well,\. go ahead and praise me all ya like.\.\. I ain't a dancer,\. though.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Your fur is so strange~\. Never seen anything like it before!\.\. Can we touch touch?\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Wah!~\.\.\. Scary,\. scary!~\.\.\. Might have to touch touch when she's not looking...\.\.\.~\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Grr...\.\.\. you're plannin' something,\. I know it...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I can hear you,\. ya little brat!\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Do you like our home,\. Miss Miss?\.\. It is our village,\. yes!~\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Ugh,\. what is it with all of you in here...?\.\. This really where you all gather up?\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>\n<Lili>We live here,\. but not all Lili live here!\.\. Lili are everywhere!\.\. All around the Hole!~\.\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Ugh,\. why am I even asking you anything?\.\. Forget it.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Huh...\.\.\. so there's more of you out there?\.\.

<\v[397]> s[\v[320]] n<\v[319]>
<Lili>
<Lili>Don't know about that!~\.\.\. But I know there's other places!\.\. My friend lives deep below!~\.\.\. Near the big rock people!~\.\. n<GameFont> s[30]
This chest is huge!!\.\. But maybe with enough \i[324] \c[18]Strength\c[0] you'd be able to open it...
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Where'd you get \i[350] that thing there?~\.\.\. Is it magical?\.\. It looks important~\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Eh?\.\. What're you pointing at...\.\.\. oh,\. right,\. this thing.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Is that how you became like us?\.\. Never heard of any tiny people besides the Lilis~\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Yeah.\.\. Can't say I was expecting people normally this size when I used it,\. though...\.\.\.
\n<\v[397]>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>With the cave maw gone,\. our home will be super safe now!~\.\.\. The Lili can feast and dance forever!~\.\.\.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<\n[1]>Well this one's in high spirits...\.\.\. is alcohol even a good idea to drink at this size?\.\.\.\BST[8] Eh.\.\. Whatever.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Well,\. least I can say I got my good deed for the day done.\.\.
